text:
Hello, nice day!

just asking if someone nows how to have a module with 3 text fiels that are able to edit in the design panel what can i do to also make possible to change the font size of each item?

`&lt;!-- module html --&gt;`
&lt;div class="text-center"&gt;
  &lt;div class="text-black inline-block"&gt;
    &lt;h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl"&gt;{{ module.title }}&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;hr class="h-1 mt-3 w-11/12 lg:w-1/2 border-purple" /&gt;
    &lt;h2 style="font-size: {{ module.title_s }};" class="font-bold text-lg text-purple pl-12 pr-12 lg:text-xl mt-3"&gt;{{ module.subtitle }}&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="font-Mulish text-base pl-10 pr-10 lg:text-lg mt-4"&gt;
    {{ module.paragraph }}
&lt;/div&gt;
